TITLE: Creating Browser Context Options with Viewport Configuration in Playwright
DESCRIPTION: Creates browser context options for Playwright, setting viewport dimensions based on provided width and height or using default values. This function helps in standardizing browser window configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serenity-js/serenity-js/blob/main/packages/core/spec/io/finder-examples/file1.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
/**
 * @package
 */
export function browserContextOptionsFor(options: { width?: number, height?: number } = {}): object {
    const { width, height } = options;

    return {
        viewport: {
            width:  width  || DEFAULT_BROWSER_WIDTH,
            height: height || DEFAULT_BROWSER_HEIGHT,
        },
    };
}
```

