TITLE: Configuring Lerna for Serenity/JS Package Management
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures Lerna for managing the Serenity/JS project as a monorepo. It specifies the version, package locations, and npm client settings for the project.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serenity-js/serenity-js/blob/main/packages/core/spec/io/finder-examples/nested/file3.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "version": "3.1.1",
  "packages": [
    "packages/*"
  ],
  "command": {
    "version": {
      "push": false
    },
    "publish": {
      "ignoreChanges": [
        "*.md"
      ],
      "bump": "patch",
      "message": "chore(release): %s",
      "push": false
    }
  },
  "npmClient": "npm"
}
```

